OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBecoming
OL,6,Fcloudier with some light rain into
OL,7,FFriday, and conditions remaining
OL,8,Fgenerally cloudy and mild into the
OL,9,Fweekend, with further light rain at
OL,10,Ftimes.
